  "comment": "BS960 Stroboscope LED RGBW Combi: The BS960 is a powerful multi-use fixture and is specially designed to be used as a strobe, blinder or wash, thanks to the 960 SMD LEDs. The LED panel is divided in different sections and can flash in any colour you desire thanks to its RGB mixing system. This fixture is also equipped with a strip of 96 white SMD LEDs in the centre of the fixture, controllable in different sections to create the traditional look of a strobe. The BS384 makes it possible to create unique colourful effects and control is easy via DMX or in stand-alone mode with automatic function. Suitable for all kind of shows and events.\n\n",
